==職業生涯==
===密爾瓦基釀酒人===
[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，釀酒人在第三輪選進了甘格農。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.perfectgame.org/Players/PlayerProfile.aspx?ID=128904 |title=Drew Gagnon - Player Profile | Perfect Game USA |publisher=Perfectgame.org |date= |accessdate=August 18, 2018 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025081506/https://www.perfectgame.org/Players/Playerprofile.aspx?ID=128904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

甘格農先從新人聯盟開始職業生涯，防禦率為8.05。2012年他升上高階1A，隔年升上2A。2015年，他成功升上3A，2016年他投出3勝1敗，防禦率4.48。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=543193#/career/R/pitching/2018/ALL|title=Drew Gagnon Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|accessdate=July 9, 2018|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025052659/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=543193#/career/R/pitching/2018/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===洛杉磯天使===
2016年12月13日，甘格農和[[馬丁·馬唐納多|馬丁·馬唐納多]]被交易至天使，釀酒人換來Jett Bandy。<ref>{{cite web |author=J.P. Hoornstra |url=https://www.dailynews.com/2016/12/13/angels-trade-jett-bandy-to-brewers-for-martin-maldonado/ |title=Angels trade Jett Bandy to Brewers for Martin Maldonado – Daily News |publisher=Dailynews.com |date= |accessdate=August 18, 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710071328/https://www.dailynews.com/2016/12/13/angels-trade-jett-bandy-to-brewers-for-martin-maldonado/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年他在3A投出1勝1敗，防禦率6.25的成績。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://risingapple.com/2017/12/30/mets-sign-gagnon-minors/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-27 |archive-date=2018-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710133006/https://risingapple.com/2017/12/30/mets-sign-gagnon-minors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>球季結束後成為自由球員。

===紐約大都會===
2017年12月22日，甘格農與大都會簽下合約。<ref>{{cite web |author=RotoWire Staff |url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/mets-drew-gagnon-inks-deal-with-mets/ |title=Mets' Drew Gagnon: Inks deal with Mets |publisher=CBSSports.com |date=January 5, 2018 |accessdate=August 18, 2018 |archive-date=2018-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710101910/https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/mets-drew-gagnon-inks-deal-with-mets/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在2A只出賽1場比賽便被升上3A。2018年7月10日，甘格農登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Eckardt |first1=Jorge |title=Mets option Paul Sewald to Las Vegas, call up Drew Gagnon |url=https://www.amazinavenue.com/2018/7/10/17556744/new-york-mets-paul-sewald-drew-gagnon |accessdate=July 10, 2018 |work=Amazin' Avenue |publisher=[[SB_Nation|SB Nation]] |date=July 10, 2018 |archive-date=2020-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200103084230/https://www.amazinavenue.com/2018/7/10/17556744/new-york-mets-paul-sewald-drew-gagnon |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在初登板主投4.2局失6分。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Popper |first1=Daniel |title=Historically bad Mets lose 53rd game of season as Drew Gagnon gets rocked by Phillies in MLB debut |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/ny-sports-mets-phillies-gamebox-20180710-story.html |accessdate=July 10, 2018 |work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]] |date=July 10, 2018 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030060719/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/ny-sports-mets-phillies-gamebox-20180710-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年11月20日，球隊將他放進指定讓渡名單內。他也決定挑戰韓國職棒。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2019/11/mets-drew-gagnon-reportedly-working-on-kbo-deal.html|title=Mets Designate Drew Gagnon For Assignment|author=Jeff Todd|date=November 20, 2019|website=MLB Trade Rumors|accessdate=November 20, 2019|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221125142/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2019/11/mets-drew-gagnon-reportedly-working-on-kbo-deal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===起亞虎===
2019年12月10日，甘格農與起亞虎簽下1年85萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tigers.co.kr/news/news_view.asp?seq=322441|title=KIA, 외국인 투수 드류 가뇽 영입, 터커 재계약|website=[[Kia_Tigers|Kia Tigers]]|date=December 10, 2019|accessdate=December 10, 2019|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811041754/https://tigers.co.kr/news/news_view.asp?seq=322441|dead-url=no}}</ref>

